column7: There is no need to flatter me, young one. But here, may this gift ease your journey
Settrigh, you honour me again? ... Even if I cannot understand it, I can give you something equivalent.
The protection of the Spirit Realm!
I've come to offer my protection.
I'm here for you, young one.
Fight onward, Prince Settrigh, knowing I am at your side.
I wanted you to have this.
I have a gift, little one.
A token of my faith in you, little one.
Settrigh, I thought you saw truly...
Why choose this course of action?
Even my mercy may have limits.
At present I would ask for privacy.
I commend you for your efforts.
What is the meaning of this?
Noble Prince, you are going to get out of there. I'll see that all of us in the Spirit Realm do our part, beginning with me now.
What is the meaning of this?
I trusted I could count on you.
No pleasing all within the Spirit Realm, I suppose.
This is a victory for our cause.
Perhaps next time you shall cooperate with me again.
Fight against me, and even my forgiveness shall not be forthcoming.
Know that this could have been avoided, Settrigh.
Do not ask me to do this...!
Please, this is not what I intended...
